## `test_setxattr_default_flag_is_upsert(fs_with_file)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-xattrs-8 -->

### Purpose
Default `flags=0` behaves as "create-or-replace" — the POSIX default.

### Postconditions

```python
fs_with_file.setxattr("/f", "user.x", b"one")
fs_with_file.setxattr("/f", "user.x", b"two")
assert fs_with_file.getxattr("/f", "user.x") == b"two"
```

